<div class="collapse__heading">
Cwmbran Ticket Prices
</div>
<div class="collapse__content">
<div class="collapse__wrapper">
<div class="container container-tiny generic-content__text written-content">
Full T&amp;Cs for Cwmbran Ticket Prices<br />
Participating Vue Cinema: Cwmbran<br />
<br />
1. Vue Cwmbran offers three categories of seating as detailed below:<br />
a. Recliner Saver &ndash; standard seats with our lowest prices<br />
b. Recliner &ndash; standard seats<br />
c. Recliner Plus &ndash; our most comfortable seats in the best location<br />
2. Ticket prices for the different categories of seating vary by screening type such as event cinema, and are displayed on Price Lists in cinema and at www.myvue.com<br />
3. Additional 75p booking fee per ticket applies to tickets purchased online via myvue.com and via our call centre<br />
4. The number of seats in each seating category may vary by screening and may be adjusted at any time prior to screening and without notice<br />
5. The price of a ticket shall be as stated at the time of purchase<br />
6. Vue reserves the right to change prices at any time and without notice<br />
7. Additional charges apply for 3D screenings and 3D glasses<br />
8. Customers redeeming Vue/third party-issued vouchers that offer a percentage discount on the ticket price (including, but not limited to: EE Film Card) will receive the discount on the combined total of the applicable price for the selected seating category plus any additional charges (as listed above)<br />
9. Customers holding complimentary/third party tickets (including, but not limited to: Club Lloyds and Vitality) can select Saver and Regular seats for no extra charge; additional charges apply for upgrade from Regular to VIP seating<br />
10. Vue&rsquo;s Guest Admissions Policy and Ticket Terms and Conditions apply<br />
11. For details of our privacy policy go to www.myvue.com/privacy<br /></div>
