a.<span> </span>Saver &ndash; standard seats with our lowest prices<br />
b.<span> </span>Regular &ndash; standard seats&nbsp;<br />
c.<span> </span>VIP &ndash; our most comfortable seats in the best location<br />
2.<span> </span>Ticket prices for the different categories of seating vary by screening type such as event cinema, and are displayed on Price Lists in cinema and at www.myvue.com<br />
3.<span> </span>Additional 75p booking fee per ticket applies to tickets purchased online via myvue.com and via our call centre<br />
