8.<span> </span>Customers redeeming Vue/third party-issued vouchers that offer a percentage discount on the ticket price (including, but not limited to: EE Film Card) will receive the discount on the combined total of the applicable price for the selected seating category plus any additional charges (as listed above)<br />
9.<span> </span>Customers holding complimentary/third party tickets (including, but not limited to: Club Lloyds and Vitality) can select Saver and Regular seats for no extra charge; additional charges apply for upgrade from Regular to VIP seating<br />
