<div class="collapse__heading">
Vue Birkenhead and Vue Merthyr &#163;5.99 promotion
</div>
<div class="collapse__content">
<div class="collapse__wrapper">
<div class="container container-tiny generic-content__text written-content">
<p>This offer is only valid at Vue Birkenhead and Vue Merthyr.</p>
<p>Purchase a ticket for a 2D film in a standard seat and you will pay only &pound;5.99/&pound;4.99.</p>
<p>From &pound;4.99 price applies Monday-Friday before 5pm (excluding Bank Holidays).</p>
<p>From &pound;5.99 price applies Monday-Friday after 5pm and Saturday all day, Sunday all day and Bank Holidays all day.</p>
<p>From prices apply to a ticket for a 2D film in a standard seat. Additional charges apply for 3D screenings and 3D glasses.<br />
Additional 75p booking fee per ticket applies to tickets purchased online via myvue.com and via our call centre.<br />
<br />
This offer is not valid in conjunction with the following ticket packages/screenings:<br />
<br />
1 - Big Screen Events including but not limited to live, encore and recorded screenings of Comedy, Dance (including ballet), Events, Family Animation, Film Festivals, Innovation (such as lectures/talks), Knowledge (such as documentaries), Limited Releases, Music, Opera, Re-Releases, Special Previews, Sport, Theatre and TV.<br />
2 - Premieres<br />
3 - Special events&nbsp;<br />
4 - Private screenings<br />
5 - Mini Mornings&nbsp;<br />
6 - Parent and Baby screenings<br />
7 - Last Chance to See<br />
8 - Our Screen<br />
9 - Senior Screenings<br />
10 - Movie Marathons (multiple films for one price)<br />
11 - All Inclusive Family Package<br />
12 - Scene Performances<br />
13 - Gold Class<br />
14 - IMAX Screenings<br />
15 - Scene bar upgrades at Manchester Printworks<br />
16 - Any other screenings which Vue shall determine to be excluded under this Promotion<br />
