<div class="collapse__heading">
All Inclusive Family Package
</div>
<div class="collapse__content">
<div class="collapse__wrapper">
<div class="container container-tiny generic-content__text written-content">
<p>All Inclusive Family Ticket terms and conditions<br />
<br />
The All Inclusive Family Ticket is available at all Vue cinemas excluding Vue Ashbourne, Cwmbran, Dublin, Limmerick and Thanet.<br />
When purchased online at myvue.com the All Inclusive Family Ticket is available for groups of 4 with a minimum of 2 children. If purchased in cinema the package is available for a minimum of 1 adult and 2 children.&nbsp;<br />
Saving varies by cinema and is up to 20% of the total cost of tickets and food and drink items based on 2 adults and 2 children.<br />
<br />
Adults receive a regular combo which includes:<br />
1. Choice of snack from regular popcorn, regular nachos or regular hotdog<br />
2. Choice of 22oz dispensed soft drink excluding Coca-Cola Classic and Coca-Cola Freestyle, which are available for an additional cost.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Children receive a Kids Combo which includes:&nbsp;<br />
1. A choice of snack from popcorn or Monster Munch<br />
2. A choice of drink from 12oz dispensed soft drink excluding Coca-Cola Classic and Coca-Cola Freestyle, which are subject to an additional charge, 250ml bottled water or Fruit Shoot<br />
3. A choice of treat from Milky Way bar, Haribo Starmix 16g bag, Jaffa Cakes or Jelly Tots.<br />
<br />
<br />
Products excluded from this offer include:<br />
Tango Ice Blast<br />
Coca-Cola Freestyle<br />
Bottled soft drinks<br />
Hot drinks<br />
Alcoholic drinks<br />
Confectionary bags<br />
Pick and mix<br />
Ice Cream<br />
Popcorn bags<br />
Crisp bags<br />
Candy Floss tubs<br />
Snack It Combo</p>
<br />
Purchases of the All Inclusive Family Ticket will receive a voucher for food and drink products which is valid on the day of&nbsp; the booked film screening only.&nbsp;<br />
This offer is not valid in conjunction with the following ticket packages/screenings:<br />
<br />
a. Event Cinema Screenings (including but not limited to live, encore and recorded screenings of Anime, Comedy, Dance (including ballet), Events, Family Animation, Film Festivals, Innovation (such as lectures/talks), Knowledge (such as documentaries), Limited Releases, Music, Opera, Re-Releases, Special Previews, Sport, Theatre and TV)<br />
b. Premieres;&nbsp;<br />
c. Special events;&nbsp;<br />
d. Vue Extreme performances<br />
e. Mini Mornings;&nbsp;<br />
f. Meerkat Movies<br />
g. Super Monday<br />
h. EE Film Card<br />
i. 2 for 1 ticket voucher<br />
j. Mother and Baby screenings;&nbsp;<br />
k. Our Screen&nbsp;<br />
l. Senior Screenings;&nbsp;<br />
m. Movie Marathons (multiple films for one price);&nbsp;<br />
n. Any other event which Vue shall determine to be excluded under this offer.<br />
<br />
4. This offer is valid for 2D film tickets in standard seats.Additional charges apply for 3D screenings, 3D glasses, VIP and recliner seating upgrades and films shown in Xtreme screens (where applicable).<br />
There is no cash alternative.<br />
<br />
Vue reserves the right to withdraw or amend this offer at any time.<br />
Vue&rsquo;s Guest Admissions Policy and Ticket Terms and Conditions apply.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
For details of our privacy policy go to www.myvue.com/privacy<br />
