Super Monday &#163;4.99 online / &#163;5.49 in cinema
</div>
<div class="collapse__content">
<div class="collapse__wrapper">
<div class="container container-tiny generic-content__text written-content">
<p>Participating Vue Cinemas from January 15th 2019: Acton, Glasgow Fort, Islington.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
1.<span> </span>To qualify for Super Monday customers must visit myvue.com/offers/super-mondays, become a Vue Member and &lsquo;Activate&rsquo; their Super Monday code.<br />
<br />
2.<span> </span>Offer only available on Mondays excluding Bank Holidays.<br />
<br />
3.<span> </span>Super Monday tickets are not available for purchase more than 7 days in advance of the relevant film screening time. &nbsp;The Super Monday code must be quoted to staff when purchasing your tickets in order to obtain the discount.<br />
<br />
4.<span> </span>This Super Monday offer is valid for 2D film tickets in standard seats for &pound;4.99 when purchased online at myvue.com or &pound;5.49 when purchased at the cinema.<br />
<br />
5.<span> </span>Super Monday discounts are not available in conjunction with any other offer.<br />
<br />
6.<span> </span>Additional charges apply for 3D screenings, 3D glasses, VIP and recliner seating upgrades and films shown in Xtreme screens (where applicable).<br />
<br />
7.<span> </span>This offer is not valid in conjunction with the following ticket packages/screenings:<br />
<br />
a.<span> </span>Event Cinema Screenings (including but not limited to live, encore and recorded screenings of Comedy, Dance (including ballet), Events, Family Animation, Film Festivals, Innovation (such as lectures/talks), Knowledge (such as documentaries), Limited Releases, Music, Opera, Re-Releases, Special Previews, Sport, Theatre and TV)<br />
b.<span> </span>Premieres;&nbsp;<br />
c.<span> </span>Special events;&nbsp;<br />
d.<span> </span>Vue Extreme performances<br />
e.<span> </span>Mini Mornings;&nbsp;<br />
f.<span> </span>Mother and Baby screenings;&nbsp;<br />
g.<span> </span>Last Chance to See; &nbsp;<br />
h.<span> </span>Our Screen&nbsp;<br />
i.<span> </span>Senior Screenings;&nbsp;<br />
j.<span> </span>Movie Marathons (multiple films for one price);&nbsp;<br />
k.<span> </span>Any other event which Vue shall determine to be excluded under this offer.<br />
<br />
8.<span> </span>By signing up to Super Monday online you give us permission to send future Email marketing communication with details of future Super Monday offers.<br />
<br />
9.<span> </span>There is no cash alternative.<br />
<br />
10.<span> </span>Vue reserves the right to withdraw or amend this offer at any time.<br />
<br />
11.<span> </span>To unsubscribe from emails please use the unsubscribe link in the footer of Super Monday email communications<br />
<br />
12.<span> </span>Vue&rsquo;s Guest Admissions Policy and Ticket Terms and Conditions apply.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
13.<span> </span>For details of our privacy policy go to www.myvue.com/privacy<br />
<br />
14.<span> </span>Promoter: Vue Entertainment Limited, 10 Chiswick Park, 566 Chiswick High Road, London W4 5XS</p>
<p>15.&nbsp;Additional 75p booking fee per ticket applies to tickets purchased online via myvue.com and via our call centre.</p>
<p>16. Super Monday tickets cannot be purchased via the call centre.</p>
