</div>
<div class="collapse__content">
<div class="collapse__wrapper">
<div class="container container-tiny generic-content__text written-content">
Participating Vue Cinemas: Aberdeen, Accrington, Barrow, Birkenhead, Cardiff, Carlisle, Carmarthen, Cwmbran, Darlington, Edinburgh Ocean, Gateshead, Hartlepool, Hull, Lancaster, Leeds Kirkstall, Leeds Light, Manchester Lowry, Manchester Printworks, Merthyr, Newcastle Under Lyme, Redditch, Rhyl, Scunthorpe, Stirling, Swansea, Torbay and Worcester. &nbsp;<br />
<br />
Purchase three (3) regular sized food and/or beverage items at the same time from our qualifying* food and beverage products offered at our participating cinemas listed above in a single transaction and you will only pay &pound;10.99 (the &ldquo;Offer&rdquo;).<br />
<br />
Also included in this Offer at participating cinemas are our Snackit, Kids Combo and The Collection combos, pints of draft beer and/or cider and wines sold by the glass each of which count as a single qualifying product for the purposes of this Offer. Other combo products are excluded from this Offer. <br />
<br />
Customers can upgrade their purchases of regular sized products to a large size (if available for purchase) for an additional &pound;1 per Offer. Customers can upgrade the soft drink in the Snack It Combo to Tango Ice Blast for an additional &pound;1. An additional charge (charge varies according to cup size) will be charged for Coca Cola Classic soft drinks &ndash; 10p for Kids 12oz and Junior Snack it 16oz, 15p for Regular 22oz, and 20p for Large 32oz.<br />
*The following products are not included in this Offer:<br />
<br />
Extra toppings including (but not limited to) Nachos and Ben &amp; Jerry&rsquo;s toppings.<br />
Milkshake toppings.<br />
Pick N&rsquo; Mix.<br />
Any merchandising products such as popcorn tins, drinks cups and toppers, toys, clothing, books and posters. <br />
Standard sized bottles of wine and/or Prosecco.<br />
This Offer is valid in conjunction with the All Inclusive Family Package and Last Chance To See packages. It is not valid in conjunction with any other food or beverage offer, promotion or discount scheme.<br />
<br />
Vue reserves the right to limit the Offer to one Offer purchase per customer per visit.<br />
This Offer is made subject to availability.<br />
<br />
There is no cash alternative and Vue reserves the right to withdraw or amend this Offer at any time. <br />
<br />
Any returns are subject to Vue&rsquo;s returns policy from time to time in operation, with the restriction that, if you return qualifying products, to the extent that you no longer meet the eligibility conditions of this Offer then Vue reserves the right to deduct the value of the benefit of this Offer from any refund due to you.<br />
<br />
All sales of alcoholic beverages will be subject to Vue&rsquo;s Challenge 25 policy.</div>
