<li>Vue Sheffield</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>When booking tickets online (through www.myvue.com) at the cinemas listed in paragraph 1, the price you pay for each full priced standard ticket (excluding the ticket types listed in paragraph 3) will be cheaper than the price paid for the equivalent tickets purchased at the same cinema for the same film screening and for the same seating type from a till or automated ticket machine.</li>
<li>Always Cheaper Online only applies to any full priced standard ticket that is available online at www.myvue.com at the cinemas listed in paragraph 1. This excludes:
<ol class="list">
<li>Pre-purchased/complimentary/third party tickets and vouchers (including, but not limited to: Club Lloyds and Vitality). Please see the separate terms and conditions for each of our third party tickets at: https://www.myvue.com/legal/terms-and-conditions</li>
