<div class="collapse__heading">
Hold Student App Popcorn Terms and Conditions
</div>
<div class="collapse__content">
<div class="collapse__wrapper">
<div class="container container-tiny generic-content__text written-content">
<div><strong></strong>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>1. Receive a free regular box of popcorn when you present a ticket purchased at a participating Vue &nbsp;or online, for a film showing at the Vue&nbsp; in question on the same day, together with a valid Hold voucher (the &ldquo;Voucher&rdquo;) on your Hold app (the &ldquo;Offer&rdquo;). </span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>2. This Offer is valid at all Vue venues in the United Kingdom and Ireland (excluding Vue West End).</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>3. This Offer is open to customers who are 18 years or over. Employees and their immediate families (parents, spouse, partner, children, siblings, grandparents and grandchildren) of Hold or Vue, and anyone professionally connected with this Offer are not eligible to enter. </span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>4. This Offer starts on Monday 15 January 2018 and ends on Sunday 16 June 2019. </span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>5. Only one Voucher may be redeemed per customer, per day. </span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>6. The Voucher is valid for 13 days from the start of the calendar week in which the Voucher is issued.</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>7. Vue reserves the right to reject forged Vouchers.</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>8. Vue&rsquo;s decision is final in all matters relating to the Offer. </span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>9. This Offer is not valid in conjunction with any other food or beverage offer, food or beverage promotion , or food or beverage discount scheme.</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>10. This Offer is subject to availability.</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>11. Vue reserves the right to terminate or temporarily suspend this Offer in the event of technical or other difficulties that might compromise its integrity but will always endeavour to minimise the effect on customers.</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span>12. There is no cash alternative and Vue reserves the right to withdraw or amend this Offer at any time.</span></p>
