<div class="collapse__item" data-collapse-item-id="express-pick-up-pre-paid-snacks">
 <div class="container container-extra-small expand-small expand-medium expand-large">
<span id="close" data-grunticon-embed class="icon icon-arrow-down">Close</span>
<div class="collapse__heading">
Express Pick Up Pre-Paid Snacks
</div>
<div class="collapse__content">
<div class="collapse__wrapper">
<div class="container container-tiny generic-content__text written-content">
<div><strong></strong>
Vue is now offering an Express Pick Up lane which is available only at Vue Cambridge and Vue Cramlington (&ldquo;Eligible Cinemas&rdquo;). When you purchase cinema tickets online for those Eligible Cinemas, you will be offered 20% off selected snacks at those Eligible Cinemas when you pre-pay for them online at the same time as your ticket purchase. You must collect any pre-ordered snacks on or by the date of your cinema tickets.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>What is eligible for the 20% off discount?&nbsp;</strong><br />
1 - Popcorn tubs, hot dogs, nachos, soft drinks<br />
2 - Kids Combo;&nbsp;<br />
3 - Snack It Combo; and&nbsp;<br />
4 - The first Regular or Large Combo which consist of a soft drink or Classic Coke or water, and either popcorn, nachos or hot dogs.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>What is ineligible for the 20% off discount?&nbsp;</strong><br />
1 - Multiple combos are not included because a separate discount will be applied which is greater than the 20% off offer&nbsp;<br />
2 - Single or multiple Bolt Ons (which may include junior popcorn, regular nachos, Haagen-Dazs mini tub, Ben &amp;Jerry's mini tub, bagged confectionary and bagged chocolate) are not included. Again this is because a separate discount will be applied which is greater than the 20% off offer<br />
3 - Any of the following:&nbsp;<br />
<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>a - Hot drinks<br />
<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>b - Alcoholic drinks<br />
<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>c - Ben &amp; Jerry&rsquo;s ice cream counter<br />
<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>d - Pick&rsquo;n&rsquo;mix<br />
<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>e - Bagged crisps<br />
<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>f - Bagged popcorn<br />
<br />
<strong>Other exclusions</strong><br />
This offer is not valid in conjunction with the &lsquo;All Inclusive Family Ticket&rsquo;.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>How to collect your pre-paid snacks</strong><br />
Purchasers of Express Pick Up pre-paid snacks will receive a confirmation email for the chosen food and drinks products, which is only valid for collection at the Eligible Cinemas and on the date of the cinema tickets purchased at the same time.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
You may collect your pre-paid snacks at any till at the Eligible Cinemas, although Express Pick Up purchasers can use the dedicated Express Pick Up till (when it is open). The voucher can be displayed on a mobile phone or printed out.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>Availability or change to the order</strong><br />
If for any reason any of the pre-ordered items are not available at the Eligible Cinema at the time of collection, purchasers will be offered alternative products of the same or greater value, or offered a refund at the cinema.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
If you change your mind, Vue will in its sole discretion allow you to change your selected pre-paid snack for another eligible product of the same or lower price.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>Cancellation of food and drink orders&nbsp;</strong><br />
You are not entitled to cancel your purchase in respect of any food or drink items.<br />
<br />
Please also see Vue&rsquo;s <a href="~/link.aspx?_id=593AE8A42E5745259273D141B26B32C2&amp;_z=z">Online Ticket Terms</a>&nbsp;in respect of your purchase of cinema tickets.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>General</strong><br />
There is no cash alternative.<br />
Vue reserves the right to withdraw or amend this offer at any time.<br />
Vue&rsquo;s <a href="~/link.aspx?_id=593AE8A42E5745259273D141B26B32C2&amp;_z=z">Guest Admissions Policy</a>&nbsp;and <a href="~/link.aspx?_id=593AE8A42E5745259273D141B26B32C2&amp;_z=z">Online Ticket Terms</a>&nbsp;also apply.<br />
For details of our privacy policy go to <a href="~/link.aspx?_id=593AE8A42E5745259273D141B26B32C2&amp;_z=z">www.myvue.com/privacy</a><br />
<br />
Vue Entertainment Limited, 10 Chiswick Park, 566 Chiswick High Road, London W4 5XS<strong><br />
</strong></div></div>
</div>
</div>
