<div class="collapse__heading">
The Film Society
</div>
<div class="collapse__content">
<div class="collapse__wrapper">
<div class="container container-tiny generic-content__text written-content">
<p>Participating Vue venues: Eastleigh, Exeter, North Finchley and Newbury.&nbsp;</p>
<ol class="list">
<li>To be eligible for Film Society membership customers must visit myvue.com/offers, become a Film Society Member and download their Film Society QR code. Membership costs &pound;10 per person per annum.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Membership is valid for 12 months from the date of sign up.&nbsp; By signing up to Membership, Members agree to be bound by these terms and conditions.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<li>Your Film Society QR code must be shown to staff when purchasing your tickets in cinema in order to obtain the 50% off discount. The Promoter reserves the right to reject QR codes that are forged, damaged or unreadable for any reason.&nbsp; When booking online, Members must ensure they are logged into their account and select a Film Society ticket type to obtain the discount.</li>
<li>Film Society Members are entitled to 50% off one adult/senior/student/teen ticket for a 2D screening of the film in question, in a standard seat.&nbsp; &nbsp;Tickets are subject to availability.&nbsp; Child and Family Tickets are excluded from this offer.</li>
<li>A Film Society Member is entitled to a discount on 12 pre-selected films for each year of Membership. The list of films is subject to change from time to time and can be found on myvue.com in the &ldquo;Your Account&rdquo; section.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Film Society Membership is not transferable.&nbsp; Membership discounts are not available in conjunction with any other offer or screening</li>
<li>Additional charges apply for additional tickets, 3D screenings, 3D glasses, VIP seating upgrades and films shown in Xtreme screens (where applicable).</li>
<li>By signing up to Film Society Membership online you give us permission to send future Email marketing communication with details of future Film Society offers.</li>
<li>There is no cash alternative.</li>
<li>Vue reserves the right to withdraw or amend Film Society Membership at any time in the event of unforeseen circumstances beyond its reasonable control.</li>
<li>To unsubscribe from emails please use the unsubscribe link in the footer of Film Society email communications.</li>
<li>Vue&rsquo;s Guest Admissions Policy and Ticket Terms and Conditions apply.</li>
<li>For details of our privacy policy go to www.myvue.com/privacy</li>
<li>Film Society tickets cannot be purchased via the call centre.</li>
<li>These terms and conditions, and any matter arising out of or in connection with them shall be governed by English law and shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the English courts.</li>
<li>Promoter: Vue Entertainment Limited, 10 Chiswick Park, 566 Chiswick High Road, London W4 5XS.</li>
</ol>
