4.<span> </span>To enter, Facebook entrants must correctly tell us what Goose the Cat is holding in his mouth by leaving a comment on the image post. Any entrant found to use multiple Facebook accounts to enter will be ineligible.<br />
5.<span> </span>The opening date for entries is 12:00pm (GMT) on 5 March 2019 and the closing date for receipt of entries is 11:59pm (GMT) on 14 March 2019.&nbsp;<br />
