11.<span> </span>There is only one prize. The winner will receive an A2 size print of the featured illustration, a Vue gift card to the value of &pound;50 and Captain Marvel merchandise.&nbsp;<br />
12.<span> </span>The first entry drawn at random by an independent judge from all entries received by the closing date, will win. The decision of the promoter is final. No correspondence will be entered into.<br />
13.<span> </span>The winner will be notified by @VueCinemas Facebook account within 14 days of the closing date. The winner must claim their prize by responding via email confirming their full name and address within 14 days of the notification. If the prize is unclaimed after this time, it will lapse and the promoter reserves the right to offer the unclaimed prize to a substitute winner selected in accordance with the promotion rules.<br />
