<div class="collapse__heading">
Dumbo Social Media Competition
</div>
<div class="collapse__content">
<div class="collapse__wrapper">
<div class="container container-tiny generic-content__text written-content">
<p>Facebook<br />
1.<span> </span>The promoter is Vue Entertainment Limited, 10 Chiswick Park, 566 Chiswick High Road, London W4 5XS.<br />
2.<span> </span>By entering this promotion, you agree to be bound by these rules.<br />
3.<span> </span>Entrants must be aged 18 or over, and they must reside within the UK and Ireland. It is not open to employees of the Promoter, their families, agents or anyone professionally connected with the promotion.<br />
4.<span> </span>To enter, Facebook entrants must submit their picture, name and town as a comment on the video post. Any entrant found to use multiple Facebook accounts to enter will be ineligible.<br />
5.<span> </span>The opening date for entries is 12:00pm (GMT) on 15 March 2019 and the closing date for receipt of entries is 11:59pm (GMT) on 5 April 2019.&nbsp;<br />
6.<span> </span>The promotion is limited to one entry per person. No entrant may win more than one prize.<br />
7.<span> </span>No applications from agents, third parties, organised groups or applications automatically generated by computer will be accepted. No incomplete or corrupted entries will be accepted. Entries will only be accepted if they comply with all entry instructions.<br />
8.<span> </span>If any group of people elects to collaborate on a submission, they are required to designate one person as the agent of the group to enter the promotion, agree to these terms and conditions and accept the prize on behalf of the group.<br />
9.<span> </span>Entries received in connection with this promotion may be reviewed by the promoter or a third party moderator after they have been placed online to confirm they comply with these terms and conditions. The promoter reserves the right to delete or remove any published entries from the @VueCinemas Facebook account at any time without prior notice to entrants.<br />
10.<span> </span>No responsibility can be accepted for entries lost, delayed, misdirected, damaged or undelivered. Incomplete, inaudible and/or illegible entries will be disqualified. The promoter shall not be responsible for technical errors in telecommunications networks, internet access or otherwise preventing entry to any competition or prize draw.<br />
11.<span> </span>There will be 10 winners only. The winners will receive a &pound;50 Vue gift card each and their posters displayed at a Vue venue.&nbsp;<br />
12.<span> </span>A shortlist of entries received by the closing date will be curated by an independent judge and the winning entries will be chosen by a Disney representative.<br />
13.<span> </span>The winners will be notified by @VueCinemas Facebook account within 14 days of the closing date. The winner must claim their prize by responding via email confirming their full name and address within 14 days of the notification. If the prize is unclaimed after this time, it will lapse and the promoter reserves the right to offer the unclaimed prize to a substitute winner selected in accordance with the promotion rules.<br />
14.<span> </span>Prizes are as stated and are non-transferable.<br />
15.<span> </span>No cash alternatives will be offered. The promoter reserves the right to award a substitute prize of an equal or greater value where the stated prize becomes unavailable.<br />
16.<span> </span>The promoter shall not be liable for any failure or delay in performing its obligations to the winners if such delay or failure is caused by circumstances beyond its reasonable control. Neither shall the promoter be liable to the winners for any loss or damage caused, save for death or personal injury caused by the promoter or fraud by the promoter.<br />
17.<span> </span>Entrants may be required to participate in reasonable competition-related publicity without further consent or payment, such publicity including, without limitation, the entrant&rsquo;s name, entry or any information provided by the entrant. Unless stated otherwise in any specific competition terms and conditions, no entrants or winners shall be obliged to take part in any photo publicity without their prior consent.<br />
18.<span> </span>Any personal information collected by the promoter in connection with a competition will be used in accordance with the promoter&rsquo;s privacy policy.<br />
